Auto One Car Filter Test Case. Test for checking that car filter work correctly and all cars have complete information.
               Test Steps:
                   1. Open AutoOne our-cars page;
                   2. Check expected car filter;
                   3. Verify that correct check box was checked and filter chosen;
                   4. Verify that all cars were correctly filtered;
                   5. Verify that all cars have images inside the car item container;
                   6. Verify that all cars have complete information.
